---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout region="na" title="Pricing">
  <section id="pricing" class="py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">
          Pricing
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600">
          Transparent, all-inclusive pricing in USD. Travel and reporting are
          included in every visit, so you see one number and know your exposure up
          front. Most clients use monthly bundles for predictable capacity; single
          visits are available as a lighter-weight entry option.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500">
          Pricing below applies across the U.S. &amp; Canada for typical commercial sites
          up to <span class="font-semibold">10,000 sq ft</span>. Larger or unusually
          complex facilities, very remote locations, or sites requiring overnight
          stays may be quoted separately. In rare cases where travel falls outside
          normal patterns, incremental costs may be passed through at cost and
          agreed with you in advance.
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- Single visit card -->
      <div class="mt-10">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">
          Single-visit option
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-4 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,2fr)_minmax(0,3fr)]">
          <!-- Basic single visit -->
          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:ring-2 hover:ring-accent/30 hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
            <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-3">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
                  Site Reality Pack &mdash; Single Visit (Basic)
                </h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
                  One-off visit when you need visuals and key facts without committing
                  to a bundle.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">From</p>
                <p class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
                  $1,500
                </p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">per visit</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <li>Weekday, daytime visit for a single site (up to 10,000 sq ft).</li>
              <li>Core photo set and 360&deg; / digital twin walkthrough.</li>
              <li>Headline fixture &amp; services counts (lights, diffusers, sprinklers, WCs, key equipment).</li>
              <li>
                Concise snapshot report summarising key conditions, upsides, and concerns.
              </li>
              <li class="font-medium">
                Ideal for quick checks and simple decisions &mdash; heavier reporting
                and drone coverage available as add-ons.
              </li>
            </ul>

            <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-500">
              "From" pricing assumes typical commercial sites in major markets, up to
              10,000 sq ft, with weekday access. Remote or complex sites, night/weekend
              access, enhanced narrative reporting, drone capture, and stakeholder
              representation may be quoted at a higher rate and agreed in advance.
            </p>

            <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500">
              Rush delivery is billed at <span class="font-semibold">+25%</span> of the
              applicable visit rate. Night (6pm&ndash;6am) or weekend access is billed
              at <span class="font-semibold">+50%</span>.
            </p>
          </article>

          <!-- What's included in every visit -->
          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-slate-300 bg-slate-50/80 p-6 transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:ring-2 hover:ring-accent/30 hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-700">
              Included in every visit
            </h3>
            <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <li>Pre-visit coordination with your team and building / site management.</li>
              <li>On-site capture of architectural, MEP, and access conditions.</li>
              <li>Digital twin or 360&deg; walkthrough for remote stakeholders.</li>
              <li>Labeled photo set covering shell, core, services, and issues.</li>
              <li>
                Fixture &amp; services counts appropriate to the level of service
                (snapshot for Basic single visits; full counts for bundles).
              </li>
              <li>
                Option to operate fully <span class="font-semibold">white-label</span> as part of your team
                (logo, templates, PPE, and email signature aligned to your brand).
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">
              Full narrative reporting, drone coverage, and stakeholder representation
              are <span class="font-semibold">included in monthly bundles</span> and
              available as add-ons to single visits.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Monthly bundles -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">
          Monthly bundles
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
          For landlords, funds, and occupiers running multiple projects a month,
          bundled capacity makes planning simple. Each bundle includes a fixed number
          of full Site Reality visits; <span class="font-semibold">extra visits are
          billed at $2,000 each</span>. Bundle pricing is all-inclusive: travel,
          full reporting, and drone coverage are built in.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
          <!-- Core 8 -->
          <article class="flex h-full flex-col rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:ring-2 hover:ring-accent/30 hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
            <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-3">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
                  Core 8
                </h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
                  For steady, regional activity.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">
                  8 visits / month
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-1">
              <p class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
                $14,400
              </p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">/ month</p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">
              Effective rate: $1,800 per visit
            </p>

            <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <li>Up to 8 full Site Reality visits / month (each up to 10,000 sq ft).</li>
              <li>U.S. &amp; Canada coverage; travel included for typical routing.</li>
              <li>Any visit type (As-Built, Progress, Diligence).</li>
              <li>Priority scheduling within 10 business days.</li>
              <li>
                Full deliverable set on every visit:
                <span class="font-medium">digital twin, photo storyboard, full counts, detailed narrative report, and drone stills/short clips</span>
                where legal and safe to fly.
              </li>
              <li>Extra visits: <span class="font-semibold">$2,000 / visit</span></li>
            </ul>

            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">
              Rush delivery is billed at +25% of the applicable visit rate.
              Night (6pm&ndash;6am) or weekend access is billed at +50%.
            </p>
          </article>
          <!-- Growth 10 -->
          <article class="flex h-full flex-col rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:ring-2 hover:ring-accent/30 hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
            <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-3">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
                  Growth 10
                </h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
                  Ideal for active portfolios across multiple markets.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-slate-800 px-3 py-1 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-100">
                  Most popular
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-1">
              <p class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
                $16,500
              </p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">/ month</p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">
              Effective rate: $1,650 per visit
            </p>

            <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <li>Up to 10 full Site Reality visits / month (each up to 10,000 sq ft).</li>
              <li>U.S. &amp; Canada coverage; travel included for typical routing.</li>
              <li>Mix and match visit types as needed.</li>
              <li>Priority scheduling within 7 business days.</li>
              <li>
                Full deliverable set on every visit:
                <span class="font-semibold">digital twin, photo storyboard, full counts, detailed narrative report, and drone stills/short clips</span>
                where legal and safe to fly.
              </li>
              <li>Extra visits: <span class="font-semibold">$2,000 / visit</span></li>
            </ul>

            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">
              Rush delivery is billed at +25% of the applicable visit rate.
              Night (6pm&ndash;6am) or weekend access is billed at +50%.
            </p>
          </article>
          <!-- Portfolio 12 -->
          <article class="flex h-full flex-col rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:ring-2 hover:ring-accent/30 hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
            <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-3">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
                  Portfolio 12
                </h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
                  For continuous roll-outs and national programmes.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">
                  12 visits / month
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-1">
              <p class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
                $18,000
              </p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">/ month</p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">
              Effective rate: $1,500 per visit
            </p>

            <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <li>Up to 12 full Site Reality visits / month (each up to 10,000 sq ft).</li>
              <li>U.S. &amp; Canada coverage; travel included for typical routing.</li>
              <li>Designed for multi-site, multi-region portfolios.</li>
              <li>Top-priority scheduling within 5 business days.</li>
              <li>
                Full deliverable set on every visit:
                <span class="font-medium">digital twin, photo storyboard, full counts, detailed narrative report, and drone stills/short clips</span>
                where legal and safe to fly.
              </li>
              <li>Extra visits: <span class="font-semibold">$2,000 / visit</span></li>
            </ul>

            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">
              Rush delivery is billed at +25% of the applicable visit rate.
              Night (6pm&ndash;6am) or weekend access is billed at +50%.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Add-ons and notes -->
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <!-- Stakeholder Representation -->
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:ring-2 hover:ring-accent/30 hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-700">
            Stakeholder Representation
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
            On-site representation with your brokers, clients, landlords, and trades
            to align scope, budgets, and expectations around the real space.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
            <li>Host client and broker walkthroughs under your brand.</li>
            <li>Coordinate trade days to support accurate pricing and clear scope.</li>
            <li>Join presentations and design reviews as part of your delivery team.</li>
            <li>Concise follow-up summary with key agreements, RFIs, and cost risks.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">
            From <span class="font-semibold">$1,000</span> as a half-day add-on when combined
            with a Site Reality visit, or from <span class="font-semibold">$2,000</span> for a
            standalone representation day. Fully white-label by default: we're happy to
            present as your employee or team member.
          </p>
        </article>
        <!-- Drone photo & video add-on -->
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:ring-2 hover:ring-accent/30 hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-700">
            Drone photo &amp; video
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
            Focused aerial coverage to give context on roofs, sites, and surroundings.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
            <li>High-resolution roof &amp; site stills.</li>
            <li>Context views of parking, access, loading, and neighbors.</li>
            <li>Short raw video clips for internal updates &amp; investor decks.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">
            Drone coverage is <span class="font-semibold">included in all monthly bundles</span>.
            For Basic single visits, pricing is per visit based on location, airspace
            restrictions, and permissions, and will be confirmed in your quote.
          </p>
        </article>
        <!-- Custom retainers & enterprise -->
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:ring-2 hover:ring-accent/30 hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-700">
            Custom retainers &amp; enterprise
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
            Running more than 12 sites a month, or working across multiple business units?
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
            We can structure a portfolio retainer aligned to your pipeline and reporting cadence,
            including standardised templates, integration with your PM tools, and custom deliverables for
            investors and lenders.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">
            Talk to us about your portfolio and weâ€™ll recommend a simple structure that protects your time and budget.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
      <!-- CTA strip -->
      <div class="mt-12 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-6 py-8 sm:flex sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
            Not sure which option fits?
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            Share your buildings, locations, and timelines. We'll suggest the right
            mix of single visits and bundles, and send a clear, all-in proposal.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-3 sm:mt-0 sm:justify-end">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-slate-900 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-slate-800"
          >
            Talk to us about pricing
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

